  <p>Zizira’s indigenous products have been highly appreciated by Shopping Pro's customers across the country. Pepper longum (digestion friendly pepper) is one of Zizira’s top selling products. Others products include Lakhdong turmeric power, the super-hot Naga chilli—Bhoot Jalokia, Khasi black sticky rice, and organic honey. Apart from the honey, all products are unique to the Northeast of India.
